00:00:19.510 --> 00:00:21.640 align:middle line:10%
>> Let's begin now,
as we have before,

00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:24.970 align:middle line:10%
with the energy field
awareness practice.

00:00:24.970 --> 00:00:29.410 align:middle line:10%
