00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:00.790 align:middle line:84%
And move your awareness
straight up vertically,

00:01:00.790 --> 00:01:05.360 align:middle line:84%
until you find the first
energy center above your head.

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:08.410 align:middle line:84%
This is the place that was
the top of the golden triangle

00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:10.570 align:middle line:90%
in episode one.

00:01:10.570 --> 00:01:13.300 align:middle line:84%
This energy center
above your head

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:17.500 align:middle line:84%
will feel like a place of
increased light and vibration,

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:19.750 align:middle line:84%
and it will feel like
a platform where you

00:01:19.750 --> 00:01:23.630 align:middle line:90%
can rest your attention on it.

00:01:23.630 --> 00:01:26.300 align:middle line:84%
Apply zero-point centering
to the first center

00:01:26.300 --> 00:01:29.510 align:middle line:84%
above your head, which is
moving all of your energy

00:01:29.510 --> 00:01:33.620 align:middle line:84%
and attention into the
epicenter of that energy

00:01:33.620 --> 00:01:36.740 align:middle line:84%
center above your head,
then allowing its activated

00:01:36.740 --> 00:01:39.860 align:middle line:84%
energy to stream
outwards to become

00:01:39.860 --> 00:01:44.550 align:middle line:84%
a radiant golden sun of
divine light above your head.

00:01:44.550 --> 00:01:47.270 align:middle line:90%
This is the radiance technique.

00:01:47.270 --> 00:01:50.540 align:middle line:84%
Now, move your energy and
awareness to stream energy

00:01:50.540 --> 00:01:53.180 align:middle line:84%
down from that sun
above your head,

00:01:53.180 --> 00:01:57.950 align:middle line:84%
to stream that divine golden
light down into the crown

00:01:57.950 --> 00:02:00.680 align:middle line:90%
center at the top of your head.

00:02:00.680 --> 00:02:03.140 align:middle line:84%
Then begin to vertically
move your awareness

00:02:03.140 --> 00:02:07.070 align:middle line:84%
straight down the golden
thread of the central column

00:02:07.070 --> 00:02:09.530 align:middle line:90%
in the midline of the body.

00:02:09.530 --> 00:02:12.440 align:middle line:84%
As you move your awareness
down from the crown,

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:16.370 align:middle line:84%
be aware of the structures
intersecting the middle pillar,

00:02:16.370 --> 00:02:19.670 align:middle line:84%
feeling the golden thread
move through the center

00:02:19.670 --> 00:02:22.640 align:middle line:84%
of the third eye tunnel
in the cave of Brahma,

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:24.860 align:middle line:84%
which we activated
with the cubicle cross

00:02:24.860 --> 00:02:28.070 align:middle line:90%
exercise in episode two.

00:02:28.070 --> 00:02:30.350 align:middle line:84%
Move your attention
down the golden thread

00:02:30.350 --> 00:02:33.740 align:middle line:84%
