00:02:36.140 --> 00:02:40.880 align:middle line:84%
And then follow the middle
pillar down the upper chest

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:45.560 align:middle line:84%
to connect to the heart chakra
in the center of the chest.

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:48.050 align:middle line:84%
