on the vertical center

00:02:55.130 --> 00:02:57.940 align:middle line:90%
line, the middle pillar.

00:02:57.940 --> 00:03:00.550 align:middle line:84%
This downwards flow
of divine light

00:03:00.550 --> 00:03:04.270 align:middle line:84%
