the center of your heart,

00:03:17.610 --> 00:03:20.730 align:middle line:84%
experiencing and
inwardly tasting

00:03:20.730 --> 00:03:27.330 align:middle line:84%
the beautiful divine love
nectar held in your heart.

00:03:27.330 --> 00:03:30.440 align:middle line:84%
Then as you've
activated the energy

00:03:30.440 --> 00:03:32.600 align:middle line:84%
